**/.git
**/.gitignore
**/.DS_Store
**/Thumbs.db

### Node.js specific ###
**/node_modules
**/npm-debug.log*
**/yarn-debug.log*
**/yarn-error.log*
**/.env
**/.env*
**/.env.local

### Development files ###
**/test
**/tests
**/coverage
**/__mocks__
**/jest.config.js
**/.vscode
**/.idea

### Docker/Metadata ###
**/Dockerfile
**/docker-compose*
**/.dockerignore

